      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "25833-25853",
      "markText": "“没有，没有，只是荔枝吃得实在太多啦。”",
      "totalCount": 320048,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=25833&rangeEnd=25853"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_21_22296-22323",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "22296-22323",
      "markText": "“就算失败，我也想知道，自己倒在距离终点多远的地方。”",
      "totalCount": 138082,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=22296&rangeEnd=22323"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_23_16566-16611",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "16566-16611",
      "markText": "做官之道，其实就三句话：和光同尘，雨露均沾，花花轿子众人抬。一个人吃独食，是吃不长久的。”",
      "totalCount": 100432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=16566&rangeEnd=16611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_24_3807-3831",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "3807-3831",
      "markText": "这一刻，古来谄媚之臣浮现在李善德背后，齐齐鼓掌。",
      "totalCount": 84168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=3807&rangeEnd=3831"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_24_22373-22426",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "22373-22426",
      "markText": "在格眼簿子的图例里，赭点为色变，紫点为香变，朱点为味变，而墨点，则意味着荔枝发生褐变，流出汁水，彻底腐坏。",
      "totalCount": 81522,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=22373&rangeEnd=22426"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_24_4985-5033",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "4985-5033",
      "markText": "你拿了我的牌子，还要按照流程发牒，岂不坏了本相的名声？——流程那种东西，是弱者才要遵循的规矩。”",
      "totalCount": 74196,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=4985&rangeEnd=5033"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_20_927-949",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "927-949",
      "markText": "当那个消息传到上林署时，李善德正在外头看房。",
      "totalCount": 54288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=927&rangeEnd=949"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_20_2224-2261",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "2224-2261",
      "markText": "当然，佛法不可沾染铜臭，所以这香积钱的本金唤作“功德”，利息唤作“福报”。",
      "totalCount": 43128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2224&rangeEnd=2261"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_25_23564-23577",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "23564-23577",
      "markText": "我嫁的是他，又不是长安。”",
      "totalCount": 41536,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=23564&rangeEnd=23577"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_24_6698-6745",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "6698-6745",
      "markText": "李善德突然觉得很荒谬，他依足了规则，却处处碰壁；而有这么一块不在任何官牍里的牌子，却畅行无阻。",
      "totalCount": 40176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=6698&rangeEnd=6745"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_24_20369-20468",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "20369-20468",
      "markText": "李善德是做过冰政的人，很了解这个体系的秉性。每到夏日，上头说要一块冰，中间为求安全，会按十块来调拨。下头执行的人为了更安全，总得备出二十块才放心。层层加码，步步增量，至于是否会造成浪费，并没人关心。",
      "totalCount": 39664,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=20369&rangeEnd=20468"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_22_4667-4743",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "4667-4743",
      "markText": "李善德站在原地等候，面上波澜不惊，心中却有一股畅快通达之气自丹田而起，流经全身，贯通任督，直冲囟顶。原来做个恶官悍吏，效果竟堪比修道，简直可以当场飞升。",
      "totalCount": 31185,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=4667&rangeEnd=4743"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_23_15059-15140",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "15059-15140",
      "markText": "这个积年老吏查起账来，手段实在细腻，但凡勾检到要害之处，总要反复磨算。账上收进支出，每一笔皆落到实处方肯罢休。几番腾挪互抵之后，公粮才一次全数上缴，库存为之一清。",
      "totalCount": 30086,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=15059&rangeEnd=15140"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_20_17843-17878",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "17843-17878",
      "markText": "既是身临绝境，退无可退，何不向前拼死一搏，说不定还能搏出一点微茫希望。",
      "totalCount": 28848,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=17843&rangeEnd=17878"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_20_3375-3392",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "3375-3392",
      "markText": "但无论如何，有了宅子，就有了根本。",
      "totalCount": 28378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=3375&rangeEnd=3392"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_24_21918-21947",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "21918-21947",
      "markText": "他从来没这么厌恶过自己，多审视自己哪怕一眼，胃部都会翻腾。",
      "totalCount": 28368,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=21918&rangeEnd=21947"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_22_13585-13620",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "13585-13620",
      "markText": "李善德嘴角露出微笑，可随即觉得不对，他俩初次相识，还是阿翁与儿媳妇……",
      "totalCount": 27504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=13585&rangeEnd=13620"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_22_9920-9948",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "9920-9948",
      "markText": "天下熙熙，皆为利来；天下攘攘，皆为利往。谈钱有什么不好？",
      "totalCount": 26946,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=9920&rangeEnd=9948"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300003224_20_3107-3194",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "3107-3194",
      "markText": "坊口恰好有个赁驴铺子。李善德想到他今天做了如此重大的一个决定，合该庆祝一下，便咬咬牙，从锦袋里摸出十枚铜钱，想租一头健驴，又想到接下来背负的巨债，到底搁回三枚，只租了头老驴。",
      "totalCount": 26604,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300003224&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=3107&rangeEnd=3194"
    },
    {
